title: Why Lamar Jackson & Derrick Henry are special with guest Brian Baldinger
itunes:title: Why Lamar Jackson & Derrick Henry are special with guest Brian Baldinger
description:
Rhett Lewis and Bucky Brooks talk about the latest news and notes in the NFL, including Ron Rivera being fired from the Panthers (1:50) and look-ahead to the top Week 14 games (12:10). Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky are joined by NFL Network’s Brian Baldinger (21:00) to discuss why the Ravens offense is tough to stop & what makes Derrick Henry special. Rhett & Bucky preview the top prospects in Championship Week for college football (43:30) and finish with a few fan questions (1:02:55).
